						<div class="postbody">I want your opinion on the OAM cycling show in <a href="https://sites.google.com/site/picccca/nes/stuff/main.nes?attredirects=0&amp;d=1" class="postlink">this .nes file</a>. What do you think, is it good, does it look too horrible?
